iden’s Plans Don’t Cut It.</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="332"><!-- react-text: 333 -->John Washington<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="334"><!-- react-text: 335 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 336 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="337">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="338"><!-- react-empty: 339 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="340"><div data-reactid="341"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="342"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-urges-followers-risk-lives-rallies-wont-attend/" data-reactid="343"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="344"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="345"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="346"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="347"><noscript data-reactid="348"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/b2c9c56c-afe9-4ccc-8d4c-4397455ca432/b2c9c56c-afe9-4ccc-8d4c-4397455ca432.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=5da42725e1af7edf3c2cd744f22d72aa" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="349"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="350"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="351"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="352"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="353">If Trump Thinks It’s Safe for His Followers to Gather at Protests, Why Doesn’t He Attend One?</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="354"><!-- react-text: 355 -->Robert Mackey<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="356"><!-- react-text: 357 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 358 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="359">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-